{"tid":676364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土味濃！雙星推紅的四驅車","createTime":"2018-05-24T10:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T13:13:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"06e7c4f9dea8d5d24a084351f61af4db4e3d7ebf","tid":676364,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/photo/bkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180524171314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180524171314&h=c94613da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「飛啊！麥林號！」相信80後、90後的男生一定玩過迷你四驅車。最近日本雙星（TAMIYA）聯同香港模型商，竟將香港市區的士（紅的）化身成迷你四驅車，大玩本土味，令網民大讚：香港終於有手信！ <br />\n<br />\n根據偉高模型的專頁所示，該款紅的迷你四驅車是與俗稱雙星的日本田宮模型聯乘推出。車身貼上了「的士TAXI」、「5 SEATS」等富有香港的士特色的貼紙，更配上灰色輪胎及電鍍銀色胎鈴，令外形更為像真。模型包裝盒更用上香港著名景點獅子山及繁忙的夜間公路作主題。 <br />\n<br />\n消息一出，不少網民紛紛留言讚好，「有detail（細節）位，幾有誠意」、「係咪向紅跑（的士）致敬」，又有人笑言「要自製暫停載客個牌先得」、「呢架唔拒載」。 <br />\n<br />\n該模型商負責人回覆《港呢啲》查詢表示，對於紅的四驅車惹來網民極大回響，感到驚訝，並指該款四驅車由與日本廠方相談到面世，足足籌備了約一年時間。 <br />\n<br />\n至於為何會選擇紅的，負責人稱是因為紅的在香港十分常見，可以代表到香港，加上外形適合四驅車的設計，「小巴外形太大，裝咗落底盤會翻車！」負責人指，如果今次銷情理想，未來會考慮推出綠的或藍的。該款四驅車將於6月上旬限量發售，售價為120港元。 <br />\n<br />\n日本模型車大玩香港本土情懷，早前日本著名玩具商Tomica更與九巴合作，將於今屆香港玩具節推出香港懷舊九巴模型車。外形參照七、八十年代服役的丹拿/利蘭珍寶型號設計，懷舊迷唔好錯過！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/photo/bkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180524171314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180524171314&h=486376fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/bkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180524%2Fbkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001.html&d=vS6jpcaqlwLAjihyyT9lsTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5fa0b615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/bkn-20180524170932347-0524_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"372a1018cc2d72a168367bf9b56a81f8354c0ec4","tid":676364,"uid":39855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"竟然冇van仔佬"},{"pid":"2484f7d890af12cfa84be961ed2fc32edb4302d4","tid":676364,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"紅Van四驅車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b576475262b93d27c60cbc318bd877380e9a3fb","tid":676364,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba13ec66467370b00d0c67278de17f9ec8533efe","tid":676364,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:56:10.000Z","msg":"jm7"},{"pid":"cfca02a5b06944a0f3e5972270ccaa96816ad0e5","tid":676364,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b576475262b93d27c60cbc318bd877380e9a3fb","tid":676364,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"都係雞摩架喇 就算送特別摩都唔會去到 紅/綠/白/黑個種級數"},{"pid":"adc97e73f7addaa555432203d7a62efcca036e6b","tid":676364,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"個post咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7838b4fd9280debee308e6360f21ce03a1544440","tid":676364,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hd.wallpaperswide.com/thumbs/shut_up_and_take_my_money-t2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih